column2: SELECT   p.objid AS CATID,   p.ra AS RA,   p.dec AS DEC,    (sqrt(power(p.petroR5#_r, #)/p.expAB_r - #*power(psffwhm_r, #))   ) AS Re,          s.z AS z,            p.cModelMag_u AS GAL_MAG_U,    p.cModelMag_g AS GAL_MAG_G,   p.cModelMag_r AS GAL_MAG_R,   p.cModelMag_i AS GAL_MAG_I,   p.petroMag_r + #*log1#(#*power(p.petroR5#_r, #)) AS GAL_RE_R,    (#-p.expAB_r) AS Ellipticity_r,   p.fracDeV_r AS fracDeV_r into mydb.MyTable_# from PhotoObj AS p   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE    ((p.type = #)                AND (p.ra BETWEEN # AND #)      AND (p.dec BETWEEN # AND #)      AND p.petroMag_r < #      AND power(p.petroR5#_r, #)/p.expAB_r >= #*power(psffwhm_r, #)         )
